hy nwnk! pRBU Awp (jIvW nUM) pYdw krdw hY qy Awp hI (iehnW nUM) vKo vK (suBwau vwly) r`Kdw hY;
(pr) sB jIvW dw Ksm iek (Awp) hI hY (ies vwsqy) iksy jIv nUM BYVw nhIN AwiKAw jw skdw[
pRBU Awp hI sB jIvW dw Ksm hY, (Awp hI jIvW nUM) DMDy ivc joV ky (Awp hI) vyK irhw hY;
koeI jIv (mwieAw dy DMDy qoN) bicAw hoieAw nhIN, iksy nUM QoVHw qy iksy nUM bhuqw (DMDw aus ny cmoiVAw hoieAw) hY[
(jIv jgq ivc) ^wlI-h`Q AwauNdy hn qy ^wlI-h`Q (ieQoN) qur jWdy hn, ieh vyK ky BI (mwieAw dy) iKlwr iKlwrI jWdy hn[
hy nwnk! (ieQoN jw ky) prlok ivc ikhVI kwr (krn nUM) imlygI-(ies sMbMDI pRBU dw) hukm nhIN jwixAw jw skdw ]1]
