BWq BWq dy srIr bxw bxw ky pRBU Awp hI jIvW nUM (jgq ivc) G`ldw hY qy (iPr ieQoN) lY jWdw hY;
pRBU Awp hI pYdw krdw hY Awp hI nws krdw hY, ieh keI iksmW dy (jIvW dy) rUp Awp hI bxWdw hY[
ieh swry hI jIv (jo jgq ivc) qurdy iPrdy hn (ieh swry pRBU dy dr dy) mMgqy hn, pRBU Awp hI iehnW nUM ^Yr pWdw hY[
hryk jIv dw bolxw c`lxw igxy-imQy smy leI hY, kwhdy leI ieh m`lW m`lIAW jw rhIAW hn?
nwnk AwK ky suxWdw hY ik Akl dI mMnI-pRmMnI isry dI g`l iehI hY;
BwvyN hor jo kuJ BI koeI AwKy (ipAw AwKy, Asl g`l ieh hY ik) hryk dy Awpxy kIqy krmW Anuswr inbyVw huMdw hY ]2]
