(pRBU dI jgq-rcnw ivc) koeI mnu`K gurU dy snmuK hY ieh kOqk BI aus (pRBU) ny (hI) rcwieAw hY (gurmuiK mnu`K ivc pRBU ny Awpxy) gux prgt kIqy hn,
(ijn@W dI brkiq nwl auh gurmuiK) sdw siqgurU dI bwxI aucwrdw hY qy pRBU nUM mn ivc vsweI r`Kdw hY,
aus dy AMdr r`bI joiq jg pYNdI hY, (aus dy AMdroN) mwieAw (dw hnyrw) dUr ho jWdw hY qy Btkxw mu`k jWdI hY (Bwv, izMdgI dy rwh qy auh mwieAw dy hnyry ivc Tyfy nhIN KWdw)[
ijn@W dy BwgW ivc (ipClI kIqI) nyk kmweI hY (auhnW nUM pRBU) mhW purK siqgurU imlw dyNdw hY;
qy, hy nwnk! auh Awqmk Afolqw ivc it`k ky (pRBU ivc) imly rihMdy hn, pRBU dy nwm ivc itky rihMdy hn ]2]
