Swh (-pRBU) dy (G`ly hoey jo jo jIv-) vpwrI (Swh pwsoN) qur pYNdy hn (qy ieQy jgq ivc AwauNdy hn, auhnW nUM pRBU auhnW dy kIqy krmW Anuswr m`Qy qy) iliKAw hoieAw lyK nwl dy ky qordw hY[
aus ilKy lyK Anuswr pRBU dw hukm vrqdw hY qy nwm-rUp v`Kr sMBwl leIdw hY[
