(dohW iDrW ivcoN) G`t cIz iksy ny nhIN mMgI (Bwv, nwm-vpwrIAW nUM 'nwm' bhuq ipAwrw l`gdw hY qy mwieAw-DwrI nUM mwieAw)[ iPr, iehnW ivcoN SwbwSy iks ny K`tI (imhr dI nzr iksy qy hoeI)?
