Awqmw qy srIr iek`Ty ho ky iv`CuV jWdy hn, iv`CuV ky iPr imldy hn,
(Bwv) jIv jMmdy hn mrdy hn, mrdy hn iPr jMmdy hn[
(ieh jMmx mrn dw islislw ieqnw lMmw huMdw hY ik jIv ies gyV ivc) keIAW dy ipau qy keIAW dy pu`qr bxdy hn, keI (vwrI) gurU qy cyly bxdy hn[
ieh lyKw igixAw nhIN jw skdw ik jo kuJ AsIN hux AYs vyly hW ies qoN pihlW Aswfw kIh jnm sI qy AgWh kIh hovygw[
pr ieh swrw jgq (-rcnw-rUp lyKw jo iliKAw jw irhw hY ieh jIvW dy) kIqy krmW Anuswr iliKAw jWdw hY, krqwr ieh Kyf ies qrHW KyfI jw irhw hY[
mnmuK ies jnm mrn dy gyV ivc ipAw rihMdw hY qy gurmuiK ies ivcoN pwr lMG jWdw hY ikauNik, hy nwnk! imhr dw mwlk pRBU aus auqy imhr dI nzr krdw hY ]2]
